n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/speakouttaiwan.com/2016/09/22/%E7%A5%9E%E8%A9%B1%E8%88%87%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C-%E7%82%8E%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88-%E7%8D%B8%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%9E%EF%BC%8C%E9%8A%85/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fspeakouttaiwan.com%2F2016%2F09%2F22%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25BA%258C-%25E7%2582%258E%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2585%2588-%25E7%258D%25B8%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%259E%25EF%25BC%258C%25E9%258A%2585%2Famp%2F&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVexOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=687dbf2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/speakouttaiwan.com/2016/09/22/%E7%A5%9E%E8%A9%B1%E8%88%87%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C-%E7%82%8E%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88-%E7%8D%B8%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%9E%EF%BC%8C%E9%8A%85/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"f1c7c60d49ee87764f3eb201c1d13f30e743b1f3","tid":410563,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神話與歷史之二 炎黃子孫的祖先 &mdash;&ndash;獸身人語，銅頭鐵額，食沙石子<br />\n<br />\n蚩尤與黃帝的關係雖然複雜，但蚩尤長得個什麼樣子呢？張守節撰的《史記正義》說：｢<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃帝攝政，有蚩尤兄弟八十一人，並獸身人語，銅頭鐵額，食沙石子，&hellip;.黃帝以仁義不能禁止蚩尤，乃仰天而嘆。天遣玄女下授黃帝兵信神符，制服蚩尤。帝因使之主兵，以制八方｣。而據傳黃帝有四面，容他觀四方。真的是個四面金剛。看來是越來越神奇了。</span></span>而這段荒誕神奇而不可考的｢歷史｣竟也上了《史記》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/speakouttaiwan.com/2016/09/22/%E7%A5%9E%E8%A9%B1%E8%88%87%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%8C-%E7%82%8E%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E5%AD%AB%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%96%E5%85%88-%E7%8D%B8%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%9E%EF%BC%8C%E9%8A%85/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fspeakouttaiwan.com%2F2016%2F09%2F22%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B